wiki.content: In April 2012 Brighton boy Conor Maynard's debut single “Can't Say No” shot to the No.2 spot in the UK single chart in April 2012. This year he has already won MTV UK's “Brand New For 2012” award and a silver clef “Best Newcomer” award... and did you know his fans call themselves “Mayniacs”.
